{"tid":1519963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港現正在中共權鬥的風眼，香港人想贏必須保持理性","createTime":"2019-08-30T16:27:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T16:39:49.000Z","uid":277679,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"110618f7b080364d916a3b89f642a05463f81901","tid":1519963,"uid":277679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:27:55.000Z","msg":"中共權鬥越演越烈，正利用大規模搜捕，激發示威者上街。831將會有鬼扮示威者發動恐怖襲擊，那樣就可以迫使中央出手鎮壓香港，那樣中國香港經濟攬抄，如此亂局習帝才有機會倒台。<br />\n<br />\n香港人在風眼之中，緊記如831出現任何人仕發動恐怖襲擊既跡象，勇武及和理非都必需立即離開現場及回家，因為他們正正是想嫁禍俾示威者。沒有示威者在現場，他們便無法可施。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，be water, be wise<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d37be2468501d11e440369df06c5432f4a1ea44","tid":1519963,"uid":146521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:28:37.000Z","msg":"唔好俾大搜捕嚇到，入嚟同我一齊FF，聽日一齊行落去。<br />\n<br />\n每次我一攰　就會FF嗰一日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1481098\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1481098</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"89828898fda1b2494cc784914f30bb0b190a1273","tid":1519963,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:29:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qw3QgZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQw3QgZA.jpg&h=c3ca146d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0uQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=e8acf0ff\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0uQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=81aca553\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2